strapiEvent.name: Green Roof Design Workshop
strapiEvent.location: Botanical Garden of the Ozarks - Fayetteville, AR
strapiEvent.description:
Join us in this interactive workshop where you will learn how to design and build a green roof. Lee Porter of Ozark Green Roofs will be walking us through the basics of designing and installing a green roof. We will discuss factors such as plants, materials, and installation details. 

$15/members or $25/nonmembers
